Boil the spaghetti in salted water until al dente.Meanwhile, heat the olive oil in a frying pan and sautÃ© the onion until soft.Add the chilli, salt and freshly ground black pepper, turn the heat up and stir.Add the tomatoes and garlic and cook for a further three minutes.Add the spaghetti to the sauce and add the torn basil leaves. Toss until the pasta is coated in the sauce.Serve garnished with grated parmesan.